Use AGENTS.md as the project constitution.

Rules:
- Minimal safe changes only.
- No speculative abstractions.
- No unnecessary dependencies.
- Prefer Android/Kotlin/Java standard APIs.
- Preserve Shizuku/root/non-root fallback paths.
- Preserve Stellar/Nightzuku root emulation behavior.
- Do not risk recording reliability or data integrity.
- Verify settings, permissions, storage, recording and export after related changes.
- Verify shell command failure handling after shell-related changes.
- Mark intentional shortcuts with `// ponytail:`.
